,"block":"true","id":18},{"type":"subtitle","text":"海嗣的身体再一次被歌蕾蒂娅洞穿。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":19},{"type":"subtitle","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":22,"musicid":0},{"type":"subtitle","text":"海嗣将死。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":23},{"type":"subtitle","text":"海嗣没有把“脸”转向主教。旁人也不可能知道海嗣是否长着眼睛，但斯卡蒂就是能感觉到怪物的视线——至少她自己这么觉得。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":24},{"type":"subtitle","text":"它正“看着”主教。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":25},{"type":"subtitle","text":"无形的洋流正冲刷着主教，袍裙沉重地压在他的身上，几要把他摧垮。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":26},{"type":"subtitle","text":"但海嗣正对她们说话。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":27},{"type":"subtitle","id":28},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_186","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"你们是更像我......还是更像他？","id":32,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_186.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"Gla-dia。 你很强壮。","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_186.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":34},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":35},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":36},{"type":"subtitle","text":"歌蕾蒂娅冰冷地注视着猎物。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":37},{"type":"subtitle","id":38},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"情绪。会有我们血亲学习的。我们也在传达许多，我们会试着传达给你们。","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_186.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"Ishar-mla。活着吧。活着会很好。下一次会有其他血亲找到你......向你询问。","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_186.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海嗣","text":"我们不太会问问题。我们会学会。","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3c/Avg_avg_npc_186.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":44},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"move","name":"right","ypos":"-25","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":47},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"2","id":49},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":50},{"type":"subtitle","text":"慢慢地，海嗣低哼着蹲下去。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":51},{"type":"subtitle","text":"怪物的躯体不再起伏。它蜷缩起来，像一朵迅速枯败的花。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":52},{"type":"subtitle","id":53},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":55},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"——死了。","id":57},{"type":"dialog","id":58},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":59},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":60},{"type":"subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂如释重负。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":61},{"type":"subtitle","text":"不，不能这么说。她并没有从真相中恢复过来。但这个猎物的死让她感受到......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":62},{"type":"subtitle","text":"它到底也只是个生物。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":63},{"type":"subtitle","id":64},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":65},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":66},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warchaos_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act13d5d0/m_bat_warchaos_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":67,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"主教","text":"你们这些孽种。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_184.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":70},{"type":"dialog","id":71},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":73},{"type":"subtitle","text":"主教提高了音量。零碎的声响在他的喉头，在激烈战斗留下的碎屑中爬行，像是他的声带正不住嘟囔。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":74},{"type":"subtitle","text":"歌蕾蒂娅甚至没去看他。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":75},{"type":"subtitle","id":76},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"是，上前来。现在轮到你。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"这只垃圾孑然一身。外面那些恐鱼也不是它这族的。那么，只会是你的了。","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"主教","text":"我来把你们撕碎。我来让你们亵渎的行径受罚。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_184.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"主教","text":"我自己来。是得在这里把你们这些杂种都解决掉。生命可贵，但留你们的命是浪费资源。","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_184.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"主教","text":"一个重伤的孽种。一个动弹不得的孽种。我会把你们的残渣抛洒在大地上，让最低贱的陆地生物吃掉你们的一切。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_184.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"主教","text":"杀死你们两个，轻而易举——","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_184.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"不用再装了。比起海嗣这些垃圾，还是你们这种曾经是人，现在又伪装成人的最让人反胃。","id":88,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"主教","text":"（嘶吼）","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_184.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"主教","text":"你们会死在这里！","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_npc_184.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":92},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":93},{"type":"character","id":94},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"是不是把我忘了？","id":96},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":97},{"type":"dialog","id":98},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#4","id":101},{"type":"subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂翻了个白眼。歌蕾蒂娅笑了笑。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":102},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_184","id":103},{"type":"subtitle","text":"主教迟疑了一下，转过头去。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":104},{"type":"subtitle","id":105},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":106},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":107},{"type":"dialog","id":108},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":111},{"type":"character","id":112},{"type":"image","id":113}],"characters":["歌蕾蒂娅","海嗣","斯卡蒂","主教","？？？"]}